Upon entry you'll notice the display of grilled chickens being cooked and a long counter where you can step up and order items to go. There is no hostess, you can just grab any table you'd like. The place is organized and kept clean, the Meñu is pretty basic and straight forward, the waitresses are friendly but straight forward as well. Prices are fair and the quantity of food is ok but the quality.... not so much. Customer Restrooms where clean, this location has no Customer parking, accepts credit and debit cards, and does deliveries. Thanks and Enjoy.
